      "parameters": {
        "content": "CFG-01 Configuration\n\nPurpose\n\nCentral source for all clinic configuration.\n\nResponsibilities\n\n• Clinic information\n• Doctors\n• Schedules\n• Business hours\n• Appointment types\n• Languages\n• Timezone\n• Holidays\n• Reminder settings\n• AI configuration\n\nConsumers\n\n• MW-00 Router\n• SW-02 AI Receptionist\n• SW-03 Appointment Scheduler",
